            "text": "Museum Angkut in Batu is a must-visit for both friends and families, especially for automotive enthusiasts. The museum displays an extensive collection of vehicles from different time periods. It's not just about the exhibits; visitors can also enjoy fun photo spots, including themed areas like Buckingham Palace and Gangster Town.Throughout the day, various exciting shows are offered, such as the Cars & Costume Parade and Vehicle Live Action, making the visit even more memorable."
          }
